Getopt::Long::DescriptivePOD version 0.01
=========================================

Getopt::Long::Descriptive is a excellent way
to write parameters and usage at the same time.

This module allows to write POD at the same time too.
The idea is to write the usage in the POD of the current script
during development or test.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Carp
    English
    File::Slurp
    Params::Validate
    Perl6::Export::Attrs

